A Django app for DigiD/eHerkenning authentication flows

.. contents::

.. section-numbering::

Features
========

* SAML-based DigiD authentication flow
* SAML-based eHerkenning authentication flow
* Custom Django authentication backend
* Extensible

Getting started
===============

See the `documentation`_.

